text.section:
The Chief Executive Officer shall:
Be responsible for the overall administration of the Baltimore City Public School System;
Report directly to the board;
Be a member of the cabinet of the Mayor; and
Designate individuals with primary responsibility for each of the following functions:
Management and administration of the Baltimore City Public School System;
Assessment and accountability of the academic performance of the students in the Baltimore City Public School System;
Provision of services to students with disabilities in accordance with federal and State law;
Development and implementation of initiatives for educational reform; and
Professional hiring and development.
